reviewText: Nothing really good to say about this, basically boring
They will bet on anything, and I mean anything. Love this show, they are hilarious. This is a must watch for anyone that wants some good laughs.

Not just for gamblers or poker fans, I Bet You is what you might get if you put a buddy film, a poker game, and sheer entertainment in a blender. Esfandiari and Laak are zany and sharp and would likely make reciting the telephone book wildly entertaining. And of course, they'd find a way to bet on that too.
A lot of fun to watch. Good clean fun for the most part. Not for everyone but many will enjoy.
